
The tomcat file goes in C:\
server.xml goes in C:\Program Files\Apache Software Foundation\Tomcat 8.0\conf

restart tomcat service

to generate your own SSL cert:

    Open a Command Prompt
    cd C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_91\bin
    keytool -genkey -alias mkyong -keyalg RSA -keystore c:\mkyongkeystore

I used password "changeit" as listed in the book.